title: Razan's Organic Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Salad bar, Take-out, Mexican, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All food is freshly made-in-house using organic produce. Offers vegan choices, plus anything on menu can be customized to your liking. Located near the UC Berkeley campus. Small place with limited seating inside.
